-- Serb Farmer Who Killed 13 in Shooting Spree Dies, Blic Reports
-- B y   M i s h a   S a v i c
-- 2013-04-11T12:50:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-11/serb-farmer-who-killed-13-in-shooting-spree-dies-blic-reports.html
Ljubisa Bogdanovic, 60-year-old
Serbian farmer and war veteran who killed 13 relatives and
neighbors before shooting himself on March 9, has died,  Blic 
newspaper reported, citing a hospital source.  The man died without regaining consciousness from self-
inflicted gunshots to the head, according to the report.  His wife, who was wounded in the attack, has survived the
gunshot wound to her neck, acoring to Tanjug newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story: Misha Savic in Belgrade
at   msavic2@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
